name: Such A Good Time
description:
Such A Good Time

Item №2 / 4
SWEET NOCTURNES series 

Night is the time when the soul reveals its true sides, when you can dream and think about everything, look at the quiet nature without the hustle of the day. 

"Sweet Nocturnes" series contains 4 songs recorded in different and custom tuning each. This is complete improvisation takes,  recorded without rehearsals.

I hope abstract minimalistic artworks will be a nice addition and you will like it too.
